{"tid":1259222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係發夢嘅同時，我地咁多位都要支持連仔連尼住","createTime":"2019-06-26T13:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T17:19:08.000Z","uid":85051,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08deb5093a747451249c2ef2c963a7165af79d18","tid":1259222,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，我只係一個小小嘅巴打<br />\n未必話有好大嘅號召力<br />\n但好希望，各位發夢嘅同時<br />\n都要俾翻啲支持俾連仔 連尼住<br />\n佢同佢嘅團隊一定受緊極大嘅壓力<br />\n因為咁多次嘅發夢 <br />\n連登嘅角色佔咗個好重要嘅角色<br />\n佢為咗我地有更流暢地開Po<br />\n放棄賺錢，暫不賣廣告<br />\n所以，希望大家可以同連仔係度講聲<br />\n<br />\n加油，連尼住先生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6781d99401c231482c16878dea0efec2ebd39ffd","tid":1259222,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"大家發夢加油"},{"pid":"8079399bedacf79dc8eac504e8539e9095d39532","tid":1259222,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:46:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c63a304de5db3e2854b05e77bbdfd48304790f2c","tid":1259222,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"香港獨立之後，連仔就係開國功臣，唔好比共狗而家利誘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77b5c8e0c1a8098e0ddec69805d5ad5e45044c9","tid":1259222,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"發完夢個啲幫手推下"},{"pid":"6a92e5e44bad98ee6ca296731a4f52a4378951c2","tid":1259222,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:19:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}